\b0\fs22 Version 1.3.0.0 of patch cleaner implements a CLI, (Command Line Interface).\par
\par
The application can now be run from the command line with the following switches:\par
\par
     /d  - This will execute with the delete action.\par
     /m - This will execute the move action with the default location as stored in your local app configuration.\par
     /m [FilePath] - This will execute the move action, where [FilePath] is the location you wish to move the files to.\par
\par
The process will write the output to the console window and also to the windows event log.\par
\par
