\b\fs28 Known Issues\par
\b0\fs22 PatchCleaner obtains a list  of known patches that are required by the computer from the Operating system. This list is then compared against all the files in the c:\\Windows\\Installer directory. Everything in the folder thta is not on the list is considered orphaned. This approach is not guaranteed to be faultless and can find "false positives", and potentially delete a patch that is required.\par
\par
